node.text:
Our 540 Color launch is BIG. We needed to do something just as big to mark the occasion. We partnered with @londonmuralfest and @dface_official to bring his latest mural to life on both the streets of London and, in a limited run, to the surface of a 540 Color Zippo lighter. 

The ultra-vivid colors and details of our 540 Color process perfectly exhibit the larger-than-life style of street art, and we’ve curated a collection of 540 Color Street Art designs featuring @marijatiurina, @pref_id, and @tristaneaton to prove it. Use the link in our bio to claim yours.
 
#zippo #lmf #londonmuralfestival #madeinusa #streetart
